00:43:57,592 --> 00:43:59,302
gets around the governor
somehow

993
00:43:59,344 --> 00:44:00,762
and they do stop you somehow,

994
00:44:00,804 --> 00:44:02,055
what'll you do?

995
00:44:04,057 --> 00:44:05,392
I don't know.

996
00:44:05,433 --> 00:44:07,018
Go back to the States,
I suppose?

997
00:44:07,060 --> 00:44:08,645
No.

998
00:44:08,687 --> 00:44:10,331
